raction with the same points and weights over the\noriginal `Finset`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.lean#L300-L302","name":"Finset.weightedVSub_indicator_subset","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.html#Finset.weightedVSub_indicator_subset","doc":"The weighted sum is unaffected by changing the weights to the\ncorresponding indicator function and adding points to the set. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.lean#L293-L295","name":"Finset.weightedVSub_congr","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.html#Finset.weightedVSub_congr","doc":"`weightedVSub` gives equal results for two families of weights and two families of points\nthat are equal on `s`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.lean#L287-L288","name":"Finset.weightedVSub_empty","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.html#Finset.weightedVSub_empty","doc":"The `weightedVSub` for an empty set is 0. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.lean#L280-L282","name":"Finset.weightedVSub_apply_const","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.html#Finset.weightedVSub_apply_const","doc":"The value of `weightedVSub`, where the given points are equal and the sum of the weights\nis 0. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.lean#L272-L274","name":"Finset.weightedVSub_eq_weightedVSub