f the base point when the sum of\nthe weights is 0. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.lean#L105-L113","name":"Finset.weightedVSubOfPoint_eq_of_weights_eq","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.html#Finset.weightedVSubOfPoint_eq_of_weights_eq","doc":"Given a family of points, if we use a member of the family as a base point, the\n`weightedVSubOfPoint` does not depend on the value of the weights at this point. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.lean#L95-L100","name":"Finset.weightedVSubOfPoint_congr","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.html#Finset.weightedVSubOfPoint_congr","doc":"`weightedVSubOfPoint` gives equal results for two families of weights and two families of\npoints that are equal on `s`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.lean#L88-L90","name":"Finset.weightedVSubOfPoint_apply_const","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.html#Finset.weightedVSubOfPoint_apply_const","doc":"The value of `weightedVSubOfPoint`, where the given points are equal. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.lean#L81-L83","name":"Finset.weightedVSubOfPoint_apply","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.html#Finset.weightedVSubOfPoint_apply","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/AffineSpace/Combination.lean#L76-L77","name":"Finset.weightedVSubOfPoint","